snippet.title: Inherent Resolve (Teaser) - Official DCS Campaign Out Now
snippet.description:
Welcome to INHERENT RESOLVE (The Official DCS Campaign) for F/A-18C Hornet + Syria Map

Coming Soon!

Join the multinational coalition in the fight against Isis - the most ruthless and violent terror organisation anywhere on earth

Made for players of ALL levels - this semi fictional DCS Campaign for the Hornet has been designed to get you into the cockpit and flying a range of immersive combat missions

You will love the straightforward, simple instructions and gameplay in these highly detailed scenarios and exciting aviation experiences

COMING SOON TO DCS - in the next beta update



Developed by LookingGlass:

Discord
https://discord.com/invite/WGEpPXKgGU
